import { Suspense } from "react";

export default function ExpertsLayout({
  children,
}: {
  children: React.ReactNode;
}) {
  return (
    <Suspense fallback={<div className="p-6 text-sm">Loading窶ｦ</div>}>
      {children}
    </Suspense>
  );
}

import Header from '../components/Header';   // 霑ｽ蜉

export const metadata: Metadata = {
  title: 'Samurai Connect',
  description: '蟆る摩螳ｶ縺ｨ逶ｸ隲・・ｒ繝ｪ繧｢繝ｫ繧ｿ繧､繝縺ｫ縺､縺ｪ縺舌・繝ｩ繝・ヨ繝輔か繝ｼ繝',

===== BEGIN: src\components\Header.tsx =====
// /src/components/Header.tsx
"use client";

import Link from "next/link";
import { useEffect, useState } from "react";
import { useRouter, usePathname } from "next/navigation";

const LS_PRO = "sc_is_pro"; // 謫ｬ莨ｼ繝ｭ繧ｰ繧､繝ｳ蛻､螳夲ｼ医Ο繝ｼ繧ｫ繝ｫ・・
export default function Header() {
  const router = useRouter();
  const pathname = usePathname();
  const [isPro, setIsPro] = useState(false);

  // 蛻晄悄繝ｭ繝ｼ繝・  useEffect(() => {
    try {
      setIsPro(localStorage.getItem(LS_PRO) === "1");
    } catch {}
  }, []);

  // 謫ｬ莨ｼ繝ｭ繧ｰ繧､繝ｳ・医う繝｡繝ｼ繧ｸ驥崎ｦ悶ヵ繧ｧ繝ｼ繧ｺ・・  const mockLogin = () => {
    try { localStorage.setItem(LS_PRO, "1"); } catch {}
    setIsPro(true);
    router.push("/pro/mypage");
  };

  const logout = () => {
    try { localStorage.removeItem(LS_PRO); } catch {}
    setIsPro(false);
    // 縺ｩ縺ｮ繝壹・繧ｸ縺九ｉ縺ｧ繧ゅヨ繝・・縺ｸ
    router.push("/");
  };

  // 繝励Ο荳ｭ縺ｯ窶懊・繝ｭ逕ｨ繝槭う繝壹・繧ｸ窶昴∈縺ｮ謌ｻ繧雁ｰ守ｷ壹ｒ蟶ｸ險ｭ
  const showProBackLink = isPro && pathname !== "/pro/mypage";

  return (
    <header className="sticky top-0 z-30 w-full border-b bg-white/80 backdrop-blur supports-[backdrop-filter]:bg-white/60">
      <div className="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl items-center justify-between gap-4 px-4 py-3">
        {/* Logo */}
        <Link href="/" className="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span className="text-lg font-extrabold tracking-tight">Samurai Connect</span>
          <span className="rounded-full bg-indigo-600/90 px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-semibold text-white">ﾎｲ</span>
        </Link>

        {/* Nav */}
        <nav className="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm">
          <Link href="/experts" className="text-zinc-700 hover:text-zinc-900">蟆る摩螳ｶ繧呈爾縺・/Link>
          <Link href="/mypage" className="text-zinc-700 hover:text-zinc-900">繝槭う繝壹・繧ｸ</Link>

          {/* 繝励Ο荳ｭ縺ｯ窶懈綾繧句ｰ守ｷ壺昴ｒ蟶ｸ譎り｡ｨ遉ｺ */}
          {showProBackLink && (
            <Link
              href="/pro/mypage"
              className="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-1.5 text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50"
              title="繝励Ο逕ｨ繝槭う繝壹・繧ｸ縺ｸ謌ｻ繧・
            >
              繝励Ο逕ｨ繝槭う繝壹・繧ｸ
            </Link>
          )}

          {/* 蜿ｳ遶ｯ縺ｮ荳ｻ繝懊ち繝ｳ・壹・繝ｭ迥ｶ諷九〒蛻・崛 */}
          {isPro ? (
            <button
              onClick={logout}
              className="rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 px-3 py-1.5 font-medium text-white hover:bg-indigo-700"
              aria-label="繝ｭ繧ｰ繧｢繧ｦ繝・
            >
              繝ｭ繧ｰ繧｢繧ｦ繝・            </button>
          ) : (
            <button
              onClick={mockLogin}
              className="rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 px-3 py-1.5 font-medium text-white hover:bg-indigo-700"
              aria-label="繝ｭ繧ｰ繧､繝ｳ"
              title="・域圻螳夲ｼ画款縺吶→繝励Ο逕ｨ繝槭う繝壹・繧ｸ縺ｸ"
            >
              繝ｭ繧ｰ繧､繝ｳ
            </button>
          )}
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>
  );
}

===== END: src\components\Header.tsx =====

===== BEGIN: src\app\pro\mypage\page.tsx =====
// /src/app/pro/mypage/page.tsx
"use client";

import { useEffect, useMemo, useState } from "react";
import Link from "next/link";
import { EXPERTS } from "@/data/experts";

/* ========================== Types & Consts ========================== */
type RequestStatus = "pending" | "accepted" | "declined" | "expired";
type InboxItem = {
  id: string;
  requesterName: string;
  topic: string;
  note?: string;
  expertName: string;
  createdAt: string;       // ISO
  expiresAt: string;       // ISO
  status: RequestStatus;
  unread: boolean;
  acceptedAt?: string;     // 蜿苓ｫｾ譎ょ綾・域悽繝壹・繧ｸ縺ｧ莉倅ｸ趣ｼ・};

type TxStatus = "paid" | "pending" | "refunded";
type Tx = {
  id: string;
  when: string;      // ISO
  client: string;
  summary: string;
  amountYen: number;
  feeYen: number;
  status: TxStatus;
};

type Reservation = {
  id: string;
  client: string;
  topic: string;
  createdAt: string;                 // ISO・亥女菫｡譎ょ綾・・  when?: string;                     // ISO・井ｺ亥ｮ壽律譎ゑｼ壹≠繧後・菴ｿ逕ｨ・・  status: "pending" | "confirmed" | "cancelled";
};

const NOW = Date.now();
const minutesFromNow = (m: number) => new Date(NOW + m * 60_000).toISOString();

/** LS Keys */
const LS_ITEMS = "sc_inbox_items_v1";
const LS_NEWBUF = "sc_inbox_new";
const BC_NAME = "sc-inbox";
const LS_UNREAD_COUNT = "inbox-unread-count";
const LS_ONLINE = "sc_pro_online_v1";
const LS_ONLINE_LOG = "sc_pro_online_log_v1";     // [{t:number,on:boolean}]
const LS_HISTORY = "pro_billing_history_v1";      // Tx[]
const LS_RESERV = "pro_reservations_v1";          // Reservation[]

/* ========================== Helpers ========================== */
const formatTime = (iso: string) =>
  new Date(iso).toLocaleString("ja-JP", { hour12: false });

function dedupe(arr: InboxItem[]): InboxItem[] {
  const seen = new Set<string>();
  const out: InboxItem[] = [];
  for (const x of arr) {
    if (seen.has(x.id)) continue;
    seen.add(x.id);
    out.push(x);
  }
  return out;
}

function toInboxItem(payload: any): InboxItem {
  // /session 縺ｮ Invite 蠖｢ { id, expertId, clientName, topic, createdAt, ttlSec, unread, note }
  if (payload && payload.expertId) {
    const exp = EXPERTS.find((e) => e.id === payload.expertId);
    const expertName = exp ? `${exp.name}・・{exp.license ?? "雉・ｼ縺ｪ縺・}・荏 : "荳肴・縺ｪ蟆る摩螳ｶ";
    const createdMs = Number(payload.createdAt) || Date.now();
    const ttlSec = Math.max(30, Math.min(600, Number(payload.ttlSec) || 180));
    return {
      id: String(payload.id),
      requesterName: String(payload.clientName || "蛹ｿ蜷阪Θ繝ｼ繧ｶ繝ｼ"),
      topic: String(payload.topic || "逶ｸ隲・′縺ゅｊ縺ｾ縺・),
      note: payload.note ? String(payload.note) : undefined,
      expertName,
      createdAt: new Date(createdMs).toISOString(),
      expiresAt: new Date(createdMs + ttlSec * 1000).toISOString(),
      status: "pending",
      unread: true,
    };
  }
  return payload as InboxItem;
}

/** 谿九ｊ繧ｫ繧ｦ繝ｳ繝医ム繧ｦ繝ｳ */
function useCountdown(expireIso: string) {
  const [remainMs, setRemainMs] = useState(
    Math.max(0, new Date(expireIso).getTime() - Date.now())
  );
  useEffect(() => {
    const id = setInterval(() => {
      setRemainMs(Math.max(0, new Date(expireIso).getTime() - Date.now()));
    }, 1000);
    return () => clearInterval(id);
  }, [expireIso]);
  const mm = String(Math.floor(remainMs / 1000 / 60)).padStart(2, "0");
  const ss = String(Math.floor((remainMs / 1000) % 60)).padStart(2, "0");
  return { remainMs, label: `${mm}:${ss}` };
}
function Countdown({ expiresAt }: { expiresAt: string }) {
  const { remainMs, label } = useCountdown(expiresAt);
  if (remainMs === 0) return <span className="text-xs font-medium text-subtle">譛滄剞蛻・ｌ</span>;
  const warn = remainMs < 60_000;
  return (
    <span
      className={`text-xs font-semibold tabular-nums ${warn ? "text-danger" : "text-foreground"}`}
      aria-live="polite"
      title={`邱蛻・ ${formatTime(expiresAt)}`}
    >
      {label}
    </span>
  );
}

/** 繧ｹ繝・・繧ｿ繧ｹ繝舌ャ繧ｸ */
function StatusBadge({ status }: { status: RequestStatus }) {
  const label: Record<RequestStatus, string> = {
    pending: "蠕・ｩ滉ｸｭ",
    accepted: "蜿苓ｫｾ",
    declined: "霎樣",
    expired: "譛滄剞蛻・ｌ",
  };
  const tone: Record<RequestStatus, string> = {
    pending: "bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 ring-1 ring-amber-200",
    accepted: "bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 ring-1 ring-emerald-200",
    declined: "bg-rose-50 text-rose-700 ring-1 ring-rose-200",
    expired: "bg-zinc-50 text-zinc-600 ring-1 ring-zinc-200",
  };
  return <span className={`badge ${tone[status]}`}>{label[status]}</span>;
}

/* ========================== MOCK Seeds (蠢・ｦ∵凾縺ｮ縺ｿ) ========================== */
const MOCK_INBOX: InboxItem[] = [
  {
    id: "REQ-24001",
    requesterName: "逕ｰ荳ｭ 闃ｱ蟄・,
    topic: "豎ｺ邂礼峩蜑阪・遽遞守嶌隲・,
    note: "蠖ｹ蜩｡蝣ｱ驟ｬ縺ｮ險ｭ螳壹↓縺､縺・※繧ゅい繝峨ヰ繧､繧ｹ蟶梧悍縺ｧ縺吶・,
    expertName: "螻ｱ逕ｰ 螟ｪ驛趣ｼ育ｨ守炊螢ｫ・・,
    createdAt: new Date(NOW - 5 * 60_000).toISOString(),
    expiresAt: minutesFromNow(3),
    status: "pending",
    unread: true,
  },
  {
    id: "REQ-24002",
    requesterName: "菴占陸 谺｡驛・,
    topic: "逶ｸ邯壹・蛻晏屓逶ｸ隲・,
    note: "螟ｧ縺ｾ縺九↑雉・肇迥ｶ豕√ｒ蜈ｱ譛峨＠縺溘＞縺ｧ縺吶・,
    expertName: "螻ｱ逕ｰ 螟ｪ驛趣ｼ育ｨ守炊螢ｫ・・,
    createdAt: new Date(NOW - 40 * 60_000).toISOString(),
    expiresAt: minutesFromNow(-10),
    status: "expired",
    unread: false,
  },
];

/* ========================== Page ========================== */
export default function ProMyPage() {
  /* -------- 繧ｪ繝ｳ繝ｩ繧､繝ｳ蛻・崛・域ｰｸ邯夲ｼ九Ο繧ｰ・・-------- */
  const [online, setOnline] = useState(false);
  useEffect(() => {
    try {
      setOnline(localStorage.getItem(LS_ONLINE) === "1");
      // 繝ｭ繧ｰ蛻晄悄蛹・      const raw = localStorage.getItem(LS_ONLINE_LOG);
      if (!raw) {
        const init = [{ t: Date.now(), on: localStorage.getItem(LS_ONLINE) === "1" }];
        localStorage.setItem(LS_ONLINE_LOG, JSON.stringify(init));
      }
    } catch {}
  }, []);
  const toggleOnline = () => {
    setOnline((v) => {
      const next = !v;
      try {
        localStorage.setItem(LS_ONLINE, next ? "1" : "0");
        const raw = localStorage.getItem(LS_ONLINE_LOG);
        const log: { t: number; on: boolean }[] = raw ? JSON.parse(raw) : [];
        log.push({ t: Date.now(), on: next });
        localStorage.setItem(LS_ONLINE_LOG, JSON.stringify(log));
      } catch {}
      return next;
    });
  };

  /* -------- 蜿嶺ｿ｡邂ｱ・医・繝ｼ繧ｸ蜀・鳩・・-------- */
  const [items, setItems] = useState<InboxItem[]>([]);
  const [q, setQ] = useState("");

  useEffect(() => {
    try {
      const raw = localStorage.getItem(LS_ITEMS);
      const parsed: InboxItem[] | null = raw ? JSON.parse(raw) : null;
      const base = Array.isArray(parsed) && parsed.length > 0 ? parsed : MOCK_INBOX;

      const bufRaw = localStorage.getItem(LS_NEWBUF);
      if (bufRaw) {
        const buf: any[] = JSON.parse(bufRaw);
        const merged = [...buf, ...base].map(toInboxItem);
        setItems(dedupe(merged));
        localStorage.removeItem(LS_NEWBUF);
      } else {
        setItems(base);
      }
    } catch {
      setItems(MOCK_INBOX);
    }
  }, []);

  useEffect(() => {
    if (typeof window === "undefined" || !("BroadcastChannel" in window)) return;
    const ch = new BroadcastChannel(BC_NAME);
    const onMsg = (ev: MessageEvent) => {
      const msg = ev.data;
      if (!msg || msg.type !== "add") return;
      setItems((prev) => dedupe([toInboxItem(msg), ...prev]));
    };
    ch.addEventListener("message", onMsg);
    return () => ch.close();
  }, []);

  // 譛滄剞蛻・ｌ閾ｪ蜍募渚譏
  useEffect(() => {
    const id = setInterval(() => {
      setItems((prev) =>
        prev.map((x) =>
          x.status === "pending" && new Date(x.expiresAt).getTime() <= Date.now()
            ? { ...x, status: "expired", unread: false }
            : x
        )
      );
    }, 5000);
    return () => clearInterval(id);
  }, []);

  // 豌ｸ邯夲ｼ区悴隱ｭ謨ｰ繧､繝吶Φ繝・  const unreadCount = useMemo(() => items.filter((x) => x.unread).length, [items]);
  useEffect(() => {
    try {
      localStorage.setItem(LS_ITEMS, JSON.stringify(items));
      localStorage.setItem(LS_UNREAD_COUNT, String(unreadCount));
    } catch {}
    if (typeof window !== "undefined") {
      window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent("inbox:unread", { detail: unreadCount }));
    }
  }, [items, unreadCount]);

  // 邨槭ｊ霎ｼ縺ｿ
  const filtered = useMemo(() => {
    const k = q.trim();
    let list = items.filter((x) => {
      const hay = `${x.requesterName} ${x.topic} ${x.note ?? ""} ${x.id}`;
      return k ? hay.includes(k) : true;
    });
    list.sort((a, b) => {
      const unreadDiff = Number(b.unread) - Number(a.unread);
      if (unreadDiff !== 0) return unreadDiff;
      return new Date(a.expiresAt).getTime() - new Date(b.expiresAt).getTime();
    });
    return list;
  }, [items, q]);

  /* -------- 蜿嶺ｿ｡邂ｱ繧｢繧ｯ繧ｷ繝ｧ繝ｳ・・cceptedAt莉倅ｸ趣ｼ・-------- */
  const onMarkRead = (id: string) =>
    setItems((prev) => prev.map((x) => (x.id === id ? { ...x, unread: false } : x)));
  const onDecline = (id: string) =>
    setItems((prev) =>
      prev.map((x) => (x.id === id ? { ...x, status: "declined", unread: false } : x))
    );
  const onAccept = (id: string) =>
    setItems((prev) =>
      prev.map((x) =>
        x.id === id ? { ...x, status: "accepted", unread: false, acceptedAt: new Date().toISOString() } : x
      )
    );

  /* -------- 螢ｲ荳奇ｼ・illing縺ｮ繝｢繝・け繝・・繧ｿ繧貞茜逕ｨ・・-------- */
  const txHistory: Tx[] = useMemo(() => {
    try {
      const raw = localStorage.getItem(LS_HISTORY);
      if (raw) return JSON.parse(raw);
    } catch {}
    // 縺ｪ縺・ｴ蜷医・霆ｽ縺・Δ繝・け
    return [
      { id: "TX-240031", when: new Date(NOW - 2 * 86400_000).toISOString(), client: "譬ｪ蠑丈ｼ夂､ｾ繧｢繝ｫ繝輔ぃ", summary: "繝ｩ繧､繝也嶌隲・ｼ・0蛻・ｼ・, amountYen: 5000, feeYen: 500, status: "paid" },
      { id: "TX-240028", when: new Date(NOW - 5 * 86400_000).toISOString(), client: "蛟倶ｺｺ繝ｦ繝ｼ繧ｶ繝ｼB", summary: "繝ｩ繧､繝也嶌隲・ｼ・0蛻・ｼ・, amountYen: 3000, feeYen: 300, status: "paid" },
      { id: "TX-240027", when: new Date(NOW - 6 * 86400_000).toISOString(), client: "蛟倶ｺｺ繝ｦ繝ｼ繧ｶ繝ｼC", summary: "逶ｸ隲・ｺ育ｴ・ｼ医く繝｣繝ｳ繧ｻ繝ｫ・・, amountYen: 3000, feeYen: 0, status: "refunded" },
    ];
  }, []);

  const revenue = useMemo(() => {
    const paid = txHistory.filter((t) => t.status === "paid");
    const byDay = new Map<string, { gross: number; fee: number }>();
    for (const t of paid) {
      const d = new Date(t.when);
      const key = `${d.getFullYear()}-${d.getMonth() + 1}-${d.getDate()}`;
      const cur = byDay.get(key) ?? { gross: 0, fee: 0 };
      cur.gross += t.amountYen;
      cur.fee += t.feeYen;
      byDay.set(key, cur);
    }
    const gross = paid.reduce((s, x) => s + x.amountYen, 0);
    const fee = paid.reduce((s, x) => s + x.feeYen, 0);
    const net = Math.max(0, gross - fee);
    // 繧ｰ繝ｩ繝慕畑・育峩霑・4譌･・・    const last14: { day: string; net: number }[] = [];
    for (let i = 13; i >= 0; i--) {
      const d = new Date(Date.now() - i * 86400_000);
      const key = `${d.getFullYear()}-${d.getMonth() + 1}-${d.getDate()}`;
      const v = byDay.get(key);
      last14.push({
        day: `${d.getMonth() + 1}/${d.getDate()}`,
        net: Math.max(0, (v?.gross ?? 0) - (v?.fee ?? 0)),
      });
    }
    return { gross, fee, net, last14 };
  }, [txHistory]);

  /* -------- 繧ｪ繝ｳ繝ｩ繧､繝ｳ遞ｼ蜒肴凾髢難ｼ医Ο繧ｰ縺九ｉ邂怜・・・-------- */
  function calcUptime(days: number) {
    try {
      const raw = localStorage.getItem(LS_ONLINE_LOG);
      const log: { t: number; on: boolean }[] = raw ? JSON.parse(raw) : [];
      const since = Date.now() - days * 86400_000;
      const seg = log.filter((e) => e.t >= since);
      const lastBefore = [...log].reverse().find((e) => e.t < since);
      if (lastBefore) seg.unshift({ t: since, on: lastBefore.on });
      if (seg.length === 0) return 0;
      let sum = 0;
      for (let i = 0; i < seg.length; i++) {
        const cur = seg[i];
        if (i === seg.length - 1) {
          // open interval until now
          if (cur.on) sum += Date.now() - cur.t;
        } else {
          const nextT = seg[i + 1].t;
          if (cur.on) sum += nextT - cur.t;
        }
      }
      return Math.max(0, Math.round(sum / 1000)); // sec
    } catch {
      return 0;
    }
  }
  const uptime7s = calcUptime(7);
  const uptime30s = calcUptime(30);

  /* -------- 莠育ｴ・ｼ域悴蜃ｦ逅・→遒ｺ螳壹ｒ縺ｾ縺ｨ繧√※邂｡逅・ｼ・-------- */
  const [reservTab, setReservTab] = useState<"pending" | "confirmed">("pending");
  const reservations: Reservation[] = useMemo(() => {
    try {
      const raw = localStorage.getItem(LS_RESERV);
      if (raw) return JSON.parse(raw);
    } catch {}
    return [
      { id: "RS-1001", client: "蟆乗棊讒・, topic: "蟆ｱ讌ｭ隕丞援縺ｮ隕狗峩縺・, createdAt: new Date(Date.now() - 26 * 3600_000).toISOString(), status: "pending" },
      { id: "RS-1002", client: "螻ｱ譛ｬ讒・, topic: "螂醍ｴ・Ξ繝薙Η繝ｼ",         createdAt: new Date(Date.now() - 3  * 3600_000).toISOString(), status: "pending" },
      { id: "RS-1003", client: "A遉ｾ",   topic: "逶ｸ邯夂嶌隲・,               createdAt: new Date(Date.now() - 2  * 86400_000).toISOString(), status: "confirmed", when: minutesFromNow(120) },
    ];
  }, []);
  const pendingList = reservations.filter(r => r.status === "pending");
  const confirmedList = useMemo(
    () =>
      reservations
        .filter(r => r.status === "confirmed")
        .sort((a, b) => new Date(a.when ?? a.createdAt).getTime() - new Date(b.when ?? b.createdAt).getTime()),
    [reservations]
  );
  const staleReservations = useMemo(
    () => pendingList.filter((r) => Date.now() - new Date(r.createdAt).getTime() > 24 * 3600_000),
    [pendingList]
  );

  /* -------- 謖・ｨ呻ｼ・譌･/30譌･・・-------- */
  function windowStats(days: number) {
    const since = Date.now() - days * 86400_000;
    const inWin = items.filter((x) => new Date(x.createdAt).getTime() >= since);
    const total = inWin.length;
    const accepted = inWin.filter((x) => x.status === "accepted").length;
    const acceptRate = total === 0 ? 0 : accepted / total;

    // 蟷ｳ蝮・ｿ懃ｭ疲凾髢難ｼ・cceptedAt縺後≠繧九ｂ縺ｮ・・    const durList = inWin
      .filter((x) => x.status === "accepted" && x.acceptedAt)
      .map((x) => new Date(x.acceptedAt!).getTime() - new Date(x.createdAt).getTime())
      .filter((ms) => ms >= 0);
    const avgMs = durList.length ? Math.round(durList.reduce((s, x) => s + x, 0) / durList.length) : 0;

    return { total, accepted, acceptRate, avgMs };
  }
  const w7 = windowStats(7);
  const w30 = windowStats(30);

  /* ========================== Render ========================== */
  return (
    <main className="sc-container py-6 space-y-8">
      {/* 繝倥ャ繝繝ｼ陦鯉ｼ壹ち繧､繝医Ν + 繧ｪ繝ｳ繝ｩ繧､繝ｳ蛻・崛 */}
      <header className="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
        <div>
          <h1 className="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">繝励Ο逕ｨ繝槭う繝壹・繧ｸ</h1>
        </div>

        <label className="inline-flex select-none items-center gap-3">
          <span className="text-sm font-medium">
            {online ? "繧ｪ繝ｳ繝ｩ繧､繝ｳ・亥女莉倅ｸｭ・・ : "繧ｪ繝輔Λ繧､繝ｳ・亥ｯｾ蠢應ｸ榊庄・・}
          </span>
          <button
            type="button"
            onClick={toggleOnline}
            aria-pressed={online}
            className={`relative h-7 w-12 rounded-full transition ${online ? "bg-emerald-500" : "bg-zinc-300"}`}
            title="繧ｪ繝ｳ繝ｩ繧､繝ｳ蛻・崛"
          >
            <span
              className={`absolute top-0.5 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-white transition ${online ? "left-6" : "left-0.5"}`}
            />
          </button>
        </label>
      </header>

      {/* ===== 1. 譁ｰ隕冗嶌隲・ｯｾ蠢懶ｼ亥ｼｷ隱ｿ陦ｨ遉ｺ・・===== */}
      <section
        id="inbox"
        className="card p-5 ring-1 ring-[color:var(--sc-ring)] border-2 border-indigo-200/60 bg-[color:var(--sc-brand-50)]/20"
      >
        <div className="mb-3 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
          <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
            <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold">譁ｰ隕冗嶌隲・ｯｾ蠢・/h2>
            <span className="badge-success">隕∝叉蟇ｾ蠢・/span>
          </div>
          <input
            value={q}
            onChange={(e) => setQ(e.target.value)}
            placeholder="讀懃ｴ｢・井ｾ晞ｼ閠・錐 / 繝医ヴ繝・け / 繝｡繝｢ / 繝ｪ繧ｯ繧ｨ繧ｹ繝・D・・
            className="input rounded-xl w-72"
            aria-label="逶ｸ隲・・讀懃ｴ｢"
          />
        </div>

        <div className="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3">
          {filtered.length === 0 && (
            <div className="card-soft border-dashed p-8 text-center text-subtle">
              縺・∪蟇ｾ蠢懊☆縺ｹ縺肴眠隕冗嶌隲・・縺ゅｊ縺ｾ縺帙ｓ縲・            </div>
          )}

          {filtered.map((item) => (
            <article
              key={item.id}
              className={`card p-4 md:p-5 transition-shadow hover:shadow ${
                item.unread ? "ring-1 ring-[color:var(--sc-ring)]" : ""
              }`}
            >
              <div className="flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
                <div className="min-w-0">
                  <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <StatusBadge status={item.status} />
                    {item.unread && <span className="badge">笳・譁ｰ逹</span>}
                    <span className="text-xs text-subtle">ID: {item.id}</span>
                  </div>
                  <h3 className="mt-2 line-clamp-1 text-base font-semibold">{item.topic}</h3>
                  <p className="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">
                    萓晞ｼ閠・ｼ嘴item.requesterName} ・・蜿嶺ｿ｡閠・ｼ嘴item.expertName}
                  </p>
                  {item.note && <p className="mt-2 line-clamp-2 text-sm">{item.note}</p>}
                  <div className="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 text-xs text-subtle">
                    <span>蜿嶺ｿ｡: {formatTime(item.createdAt)}</span>
                    <span>邱蛻・ {formatTime(item.expiresAt)}</span>
                    <Countdown expiresAt={item.expiresAt} />
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div className="flex shrink-0 flex-col items-end gap-2">
                  <button onClick={() => onMarkRead(item.id)} className="btn btn-outline text-xs">
                    譌｢隱ｭ縺ｫ縺吶ｋ
                  </button>
                  <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <button
                      onClick={() => onDecline(item.id)}
                      disabled={item.status === "declined" || item.status === "expired"}
                      className="btn btn-outline text-sm disabled:opacity-50"
                      title="霎樣"
                    >
                      霎樣
                    </button>
                    <a
                      href={`/chat/${item.id}`}
                      onClick={() => onAccept(item.id)}
                      className="btn btn-primary text-sm"
                      title="繝√Ε繝・ヨ縺ｫ蜈･螳､縺励※蟇ｾ蠢憺幕蟋・
                    >
                      蜿苓ｫｾ縺励※蜈･螳､
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* ===== 2. 莠育ｴ・ｼ域悴蜃ｦ逅・& 遒ｺ螳夲ｼ峨∪縺ｨ繧・===== */}
      <section
        id="reservations"
        className="card p-5 ring-1 ring-[color:var(--sc-ring)] border-2 border-amber-200/60 bg-amber-50/40"
      >
        <div className="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between">
          <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
            <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold">莠育ｴ・ｮ｡逅・/h2>
            {pendingList.length > 0 ? (
              <span className="badge-warning">譛ｪ蜃ｦ逅・{pendingList.length}</span>
            ) : (
              <span className="badge">譛ｪ蜃ｦ逅・↑縺・/span>
            )}
            {staleReservations.length > 0 && (
              <span className="badge-warning">24譎る俣雜・{staleReservations.length}</span>
            )}
          </div>
          <Link href="/pro/reservations" className="text-sm underline">
            荳隕ｧ繧帝幕縺・          </Link>
        </div>

        {/* 繧ｿ繝・*/}
        <div className="mb-3 inline-flex rounded-lg border bg-white p-1">
          <button
            className={`px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-md ${reservTab === "pending" ? "bg-amber-100 font-medium" : "text-subtle hover:bg-zinc-50"}`}
            onClick={() => setReservTab("pending")}
          >
            譛ｪ蜃ｦ逅・Μ繧ｯ繧ｨ繧ｹ繝・          </button>
          <button
            className={`px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-md ${reservTab === "confirmed" ? "bg-amber-100 font-medium" : "text-subtle hover:bg-zinc-50"}`}
            onClick={() => setReservTab("confirmed")}
          >
            遒ｺ螳壹せ繧ｱ繧ｸ繝･繝ｼ繝ｫ
          </button>
        </div>

        {/* 繝壹う繝ｳ */}
        {reservTab === "pending" ? (
          pendingList.length === 0 ? (
            <p className="text-sm text-subtle">譛ｪ蜃ｦ逅・・莠育ｴ・Μ繧ｯ繧ｨ繧ｹ繝医・縺ゅｊ縺ｾ縺帙ｓ縲・/p>
          ) : (
            <ul className="space-y-2">
              {pendingList.map((r) => (
                <li key={r.id} className="rounded-lg border bg-white/70 p-3 text-sm">
                  <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
                    <div className="font-medium">{r.topic}</div>
                    <span className="text-xs text-subtle">ID: {r.id}</span>
                  </div>
                  <div className="mt-1 text-subtle">
                    萓晞ｼ閠・ｼ嘴r.client} ・・蜿嶺ｿ｡・嘴formatTime(r.createdAt)}
                  </div>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          )
        ) : confirmedList.length === 0 ? (
          <p className="text-sm text-subtle">莠亥ｮ壹＆繧後※縺・ｋ髱｢隲・・縺ゅｊ縺ｾ縺帙ｓ縲・/p>
        ) : (
          <div className="overflow-x-auto">
            <table className="sc-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>譌･譎・/th>
                  <th>萓晞ｼ閠・/th>
                  <th>繝医ヴ繝・け</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                {confirmedList.map((r) => (
                  <tr key={r.id}>
                    <td>{formatTime(r.when ?? r.createdAt)}</td>
                    <td>{r.client}</td>
                    <td className="max-w-[28rem] truncate">{r.topic}</td>
                  </tr>
                ))}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        )}
      </section>

      {/* ===== 3. 縺昴・莉悶Γ繝九Η繝ｼ・井ｺ育ｴ・Μ繧ｯ繧ｨ繧ｹ繝医・蜑企勁・冗ｸｦ3繝悶Ο繝・け・・===== */}
      <section className="space-y-4">
        <Link href="/pro/history" className="card p-5 hover:shadow transition-shadow block">
          <h3 className="text-lg font-semibold">蟇ｾ蠢懷ｱ･豁ｴ</h3>
          <p className="mt-1 text-sm text-subtle">驕主悉縺ｮ逶ｸ隲・ｯｾ蠢懊ｒ讀懃ｴ｢繝ｻ遒ｺ隱阪＠縺ｾ縺吶・/p>
        </Link>

        <Link href="/pro/billing" className="card p-5 hover:shadow transition-shadow block">
          <h3 className="text-lg font-semibold">豎ｺ貂域ュ蝣ｱ</h3>
          <p className="mt-1 text-sm text-subtle">
            螢ｲ荳翫・謇区焚譁吶・謖ｯ霎ｼ莠亥ｮ壹・遒ｺ隱阪→隲区ｱよュ蝣ｱ縺ｮ險ｭ螳壹ｒ陦後＞縺ｾ縺吶・          </p>
        </Link>

        <Link href="/pro/profile" className="card p-5 hover:shadow transition-shadow block">
          <h3 className="text-lg font-semibold">繝ｦ繝ｼ繧ｶ繝ｼ邱ｨ髮・/h3>
          <p className="mt-1 text-sm text-subtle">繝励Ο繝輔ぅ繝ｼ繝ｫ繧・・髢区ュ蝣ｱ繧堤ｷｨ髮・＠縺ｾ縺吶・/p>
        </Link>
      </section>

      {/* ===== 4. 逶ｸ隲⑫PI ===== */}
      <section className="card p-5">
        <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold">逶ｸ隲⑫PI</h2>
        <div className="mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 md:grid-cols-3">
          <Metric label="逶ｴ霑・譌･縺ｮ逶ｸ隲・焚" value={w7.total} />
          <Metric label="逶ｴ霑・0譌･縺ｮ逶ｸ隲・焚" value={w30.total} />
          <Metric label="7譌･ 蜿苓ｫｾ邇・ value={`${Math.round(w7.acceptRate * 100)}%`} />
          <Metric label="30譌･ 蜿苓ｫｾ邇・ value={`${Math.round(w30.acceptRate * 100)}%`} />
          <Metric label="7譌･ 蟷ｳ蝮・ｿ懃ｭ・ value={msToLabel(w7.avgMs)} />
          <Metric label="30譌･ 蟷ｳ蝮・ｿ懃ｭ・ value={msToLabel(w30.avgMs)} />
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* ===== 5. 螢ｲ荳翫→遞ｼ蜒・===== */}
      <section className="card p-5">
        <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold">螢ｲ荳翫→遞ｼ蜒・/h2>
        <div className="mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 md:grid-cols-3">
          <Metric label="邱丞｣ｲ荳奇ｼ域髪謇輔＞貂茨ｼ・ value={`ﾂ･${revenue.gross.toLocaleString()}`} />
          <Metric label="謇区焚譁咏ｴｯ險・ value={`ﾂ･${revenue.fee.toLocaleString()}`} />
          <Metric label="謖ｯ霎ｼ莠亥ｮ夐｡・ value={`ﾂ･${revenue.net.toLocaleString()}`} />
          <Metric label="繧ｪ繝ｳ繝ｩ繧､繝ｳ遞ｼ蜒・7譌･" value={secToLabel(uptime7s)} />
          <Metric label="繧ｪ繝ｳ繝ｩ繧､繝ｳ遞ｼ蜒・30譌･" value={secToLabel(uptime30s)} />
          <div className="col-span-2 md:col-span-3">
            <Sparkline data={revenue.last14.map((d) => d.net)} caption="逶ｴ霑・4譌･縺ｮ譌･谺｡繝阪ャ繝亥｣ｲ荳・ />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  );
}

/* ========================== Small UI Components ========================== */
function Metric({ label, value }: { label: string; value: string | number }) {
  return (
    <div className="rounded-xl border p-3 bg-white/70">
      <div className="text-xs text-subtle">{label}</div>
      <div className="mt-1 text-xl font-bold tabular">{value}</div>
    </div>
  );
}

function Sparkline({ data, caption }: { data: number[]; caption?: string }) {
  const w = 260;
  const h = 48;
  const max = Math.max(1, ...data);
  const step = data.length > 1 ? w / (data.length - 1) : w;
  const points = data
    .map((v, i) => {
      const x = Math.round(i * step);
      const y = Math.round(h - (v / max) * (h - 4) - 2);
      return `${x},${y}`;
    })
    .join(" ");

  return (
    <div>
      {caption ? <div className="mb-1 text-xs text-subtle">{caption}</div> : null}
      <svg viewBox={`0 0 ${w} ${h}`} width="100%" height="48">
        <polyline points={points} fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth="2" />
      </svg>
    </div>
  );
}

/* ========================== Utils ========================== */
function msToLabel(ms: number) {
  if (!ms) return "-";
  const m = Math.floor(ms / 60000);
  const s = Math.floor((ms % 60000) / 1000);
  return m ? `${m}蛻・{s}遘蛋 : `${s}遘蛋;
}
function secToLabel(sec: number) {
  if (!sec) return "0蛻・;
  const h = Math.floor(sec / 3600);
  const m = Math.floor((sec % 3600) / 60);
  if (h) return `${h}譎る俣${m}蛻・;
  return `${m}蛻・;
}

// /src/app/mypage/page.tsx
"use client";

import { useEffect, useMemo, useState } from "react";
import Link from "next/link";

/** =========================
 *  蝙句ｮ夂ｾｩ
 *  ========================= */
type BookingItem = {
  id: string;
  expertId: string;
  expertName: string;
  startAt: number;
  endAt: number;
  status: "requested" | "confirmed" | "canceled" | "done";
};

type FavoriteItem = {
  expertId: string;
  expertName: string;
  tags?: string[];
};

type PaymentItem = {
  id: string;
  createdAt: number;
  description: string;
  amountJpy: number;
  status: "authorized" | "captured" | "refunded" | "failed";
  expertId?: string;
  expertName?: string;
};

type Profile = {
  displayName: string;
  email: string;
  phone?: string;
  preferredCategory?: string;
  area?: string;
  notificationEmail: boolean;
  notificationPush: boolean;
};

/** =========================
 *  繧ｹ繝医Ξ繝ｼ繧ｸ繧ｭ繝ｼ
 *  ========================= */
const SKEY = {
  DEMO_VER: "sc_mypage_demo_ver",
  BOOKINGS: "sc_user_bookings_v1",
  FAVS: "sc_user_favorites_v1",
  PAY: "sc_user_payments_v1",
  PROF: "sc_user_profile_v1",
} as const;

const DEMO_VERSION = "v2-20250913";

/** 豎守畑繧ｹ繝医Ξ繝ｼ繧ｸ髢｢謨ｰ */
function loadJSON<T>(key: string, fallback: T): T {
  try {
    const raw = localStorage.getItem(key);
    if (!raw) return fallback;
    return JSON.parse(raw) as T;
  } catch {
    return fallback;
  }
}
function saveJSON<T>(key: string, data: T) {
  try {
    localStorage.setItem(key, JSON.stringify(data));
  } catch {}
}

/** =========================
 *  繝・Δ繝・・繧ｿ謚募・・亥崋螳夲ｼ・ *  ========================= */
function injectDemoDataForce() {
  const now = Date.now();

  const favs: FavoriteItem[] = [
    { expertId: "E-201", expertName: "貂｡驍画ｭｦ", tags: ["遞主漁", "蜑ｵ讌ｭ"] },
    { expertId: "E-202", expertName: "螻ｱ逕ｰ螟ｪ驛・, tags: ["蜉ｴ蜍・, "蟆ｱ讌ｭ隕丞援"] },
    { expertId: "E-203", expertName: "逕ｰ蜿｣荳驛・, tags: ["螂醍ｴ・, "M&A"] },
  ];
  saveJSON(SKEY.FAVS, favs);

  const bookings: BookingItem[] = [
    {
      id: "B-DEMO-001",
      expertId: "E-210",
      expertName: "逕ｰ荳ｭ豐ｻ",
      startAt: now + 1000 * 60 * 60 * 24,
      endAt: now + 1000 * 60 * 60 * 25,
      status: "confirmed",
    },
  ];
  saveJSON(SKEY.BOOKINGS, bookings);

  const pays: PaymentItem[] = [
    {
      id: "P-DEMO-001",
      createdAt: now - 1000 * 60 * 60 * 2,
      description: "繧ｪ繝ｳ繝ｩ繧､繝ｳ逶ｸ隲・ｼ・0蛻・ｼ・,
      amountJpy: 8800,
      status: "captured",
      expertId: "E-210",
      expertName: "逕ｰ荳ｭ豐ｻ",
    },
    {
      id: "P-DEMO-002",
      createdAt: now - 1000 * 60 * 60 * 30,
      description: "莠句燕繝偵い繝ｪ繝ｳ繧ｰ・郁ｿ秘≡・・,
      amountJpy: 0,
      status: "refunded",
      expertId: "E-202",
      expertName: "螻ｱ逕ｰ螟ｪ驛・,
    },
  ];
  saveJSON(SKEY.PAY, pays);

  const prof: Profile = {
    displayName: "繧ｲ繧ｹ繝・,
    email: "guest@example.com",
    phone: "",
    preferredCategory: "遞主漁",
    area: "蜷榊商螻・,
    notificationEmail: true,
    notificationPush: false,
  };
  saveJSON(SKEY.PROF, prof);

  localStorage.setItem(SKEY.DEMO_VER, DEMO_VERSION);
}

function ensureDemoData() {
  const ver = localStorage.getItem(SKEY.DEMO_VER);
  if (ver !== DEMO_VERSION) {
    injectDemoDataForce();
    return;
  }
  if (!localStorage.getItem(SKEY.FAVS) || !localStorage.getItem(SKEY.BOOKINGS) || !localStorage.getItem(SKEY.PAY)) {
    injectDemoDataForce();
  }
}

/** =========================
 *  陦ｨ遉ｺ繝ｦ繝ｼ繝・ぅ繝ｪ繝・ぅ
 *  ========================= */
const fmtTime = (ms: number) => {
  const d = new Date(ms);
  const y = d.getFullYear();
  const m = String(d.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, "0");
  const day = String(d.getDate()).padStart(2, "0");
  const hh = String(d.getHours()).padStart(2, "0");
  const mm = String(d.getMinutes()).padStart(2, "0");
  return `${y}/${m}/${day} ${hh}:${mm}`;
};

const badge = (text: string) => (
  <span className="px-2 py-0.5 text-xs rounded-full bg-zinc-100 border border-zinc-300">{text}</span>
);

/** =========================
 *  繝壹・繧ｸ譛ｬ菴・ *  ========================= */
export default function UserMyPage() {
  const [tab, setTab] = useState<"bookings" | "favs" | "payments" | "profile">("payments");

  const [bookings, setBookings] = useState<BookingItem[]>([]);
  const [favs, setFavs] = useState<FavoriteItem[]>([]);
  const [payments, setPayments] = useState<PaymentItem[]>([]);
  const [profile, setProfile] = useState<Profile | null>(null);

  useEffect(() => {
    ensureDemoData();
    setBookings(loadJSON<BookingItem[]>(SKEY.BOOKINGS, []));
    setFavs(loadJSON<FavoriteItem[]>(SKEY.FAVS, []));
    setPayments(loadJSON<PaymentItem[]>(SKEY.PAY, []));
    setProfile(loadJSON<Profile>(SKEY.PROF, { displayName: "", email: "", notificationEmail: true, notificationPush: false } as Profile));
  }, []);

  const paymentsSorted = useMemo(
    () => [...payments].sort((a, b) => b.createdAt - a.createdAt),
    [payments]
  );

  const totalCaptured = useMemo(
    () => payments.filter((p) => p.status === "captured").reduce((sum, p) => sum + p.amountJpy, 0),
    [payments]
  );

  const removeFavorite = (expertId: string) => {
    const next = favs.filter((f) => f.expertId !== expertId);
    setFavs(next);
    saveJSON(SKEY.FAVS, next);
  };

  const updateProfile = (p: Partial<Profile>) => {
    const next = { ...(profile ?? {}), ...p } as Profile;
    setProfile(next);
    saveJSON(SKEY.PROF, next);
  };

  return (
    <main className="sc-container py-6 space-y-8">
      {/* 繝倥ャ繝繝ｼ・亥承荳翫Μ繝ｳ繧ｯ縺ｯ蜈ｨ蜑企勁・・*/}
      <header className="flex items-center justify-between">
        <h1 className="text-2xl font-bold">繝槭う繝壹・繧ｸ</h1>
        {/* 蜿ｳ荳翫・繝翫ン繧ｲ繝ｼ繧ｷ繝ｧ繝ｳ縺ｯ遨ｺ縺ｫ縺励※蟆守ｷ壹ｒ邨ｱ荳 */}
        <div />
      </header>

      {/* 繧ｿ繝・*/}
      <div className="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {[
          { key: "bookings", label: "莠育ｴ・ },
          { key: "favs", label: "縺頑ｰ励↓蜈･繧・ },
          { key: "payments", label: "謾ｯ謇輔＞繝ｻ隲区ｱ・ },
          { key: "profile", label: "繝励Ο繝輔ぅ繝ｼ繝ｫ險ｭ螳・ },
        ].map((t) => (
          <button
            key={t.key}
            onClick={() => setTab(t.key as any)}
            className={`px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border ${tab === t.key ? "bg-black text-white border-black" : "bg-white hover:bg-zinc-50"}`}
          >
            {t.label}
          </button>
        ))}
      </div>

      {/* 莠育ｴ・*/}
      {tab === "bookings" && (
        <section className="space-y-4">
          <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold">莠育ｴ・/h2>
          <ul className="space-y-3">
            {bookings.map((b) => (
              <li key={b.id} className="p-4 rounded-2xl border bg-white">
                <div className="flex justify-between">
                  <div className="font-medium">{b.expertName}</div>
                  <div className="text-sm">
                    {b.status === "confirmed" ? badge("遒ｺ螳・) : b.status === "requested" ? badge("逕ｳ隲倶ｸｭ") : b.status === "done" ? badge("螳御ｺ・) : badge("蜿匁ｶ・)}
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div className="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-600">
                  {fmtTime(b.startAt)} 縲・{fmtTime(b.endAt)}
                </div>
                <div className="mt-2">
                  <Link href={`/experts?focus=${b.expertId}`} className="text-sm underline">
                    繝励Ο繝輔ぅ繝ｼ繝ｫ繧定ｦ九ｋ
                  </Link>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </section>
      )}

      {/* 縺頑ｰ励↓蜈･繧・*/}
      {tab === "favs" && (
        <section className="space-y-4">
          <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold">縺頑ｰ励↓蜈･繧雁ｰる摩螳ｶ</h2>
          <ul className="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            {favs.map((f) => (
              <li key={f.expertId} className="p-4 rounded-2xl border bg-white">
                <div className="flex justify-between">
                  <div className="font-medium">{f.expertName}</div>
                  <button onClick={() => removeFavorite(f.expertId)} className="text-sm underline">隗｣髯､</button>
                </div>
                {f.tags?.length ? (
                  <div className="mt-1 flex flex-wrap gap-1">
                    {f.tags.map((t) => (
                      <span key={t} className="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-100 border">{t}</span>
                    ))}
                  </div>
                ) : null}
                <div className="mt-3">
                  <Link href={`/experts?focus=${f.expertId}`} className="text-sm underline">繝励Ο繝輔ぅ繝ｼ繝ｫ繧定ｦ九ｋ</Link>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </section>
      )}

      {/* 謾ｯ謇輔＞繝ｻ隲区ｱ・*/}
      {tab === "payments" && (
        <section className="space-y-4">
          <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold">謾ｯ謇輔＞繝ｻ隲区ｱ・/h2>
            <div className="text-sm text-zinc-500">豎ｺ貂育ｴｯ險・ﾂ･{totalCaptured.toLocaleString()}</div>
          </div>
          <ul className="space-y-3">
            {paymentsSorted.map((p) => (
              <li key={p.id} className="p-4 rounded-2xl border bg-white">
                <div className="flex flex-col gap-1">
                  <div className="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2">
                    <div className="text-sm text-zinc-600">{fmtTime(p.createdAt)}</div>
                    <div className="font-medium">{p.expertName ?? ""}</div>
                    <div className="text-base font-semibold">ﾂ･{p.amountJpy.toLocaleString()}</div>
                  </div>
                  <div className="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                    <div className="text-sm text-zinc-600">{p.description}</div>
                    <div className="text-sm">
                      {p.status === "captured"
                        ? badge("謾ｯ謇墓ｸ・)
                        : p.status === "authorized"
                        ? badge("荳惹ｿ｡")
                        : p.status === "refunded"
                        ? badge("霑秘≡")
                        : badge("螟ｱ謨・)}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  {p.expertId && (
                    <div className="pt-1">
                      <Link href={`/experts?focus=${p.expertId}`} className="text-xs underline">
                        蟆る摩螳ｶ繝励Ο繝輔ぅ繝ｼ繝ｫ繧定ｦ九ｋ
                      </Link>
                    </div>
                  )}
                </div>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </section>
      )}

      {/* 繝励Ο繝輔ぅ繝ｼ繝ｫ */}
      {tab === "profile" && profile && (
        <section className="space-y-4">
          <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold">繝励Ο繝輔ぅ繝ｼ繝ｫ險ｭ螳・/h2>
          <div className="grid gap-3 max-w-xl">
            <label className="grid gap-1">
              <span className="text-sm">陦ｨ遉ｺ蜷・/span>
              <input className="px-3 py-2 rounded-xl border" value={profile.displayName} onChange={(e) => updateProfile({ displayName: e.target.value })} placeholder="縺雁錐蜑・ />
            </label>
            <label className="grid gap-1">
              <span className="text-sm">繝｡繝ｼ繝ｫ</span>
              <input className="px-3 py-2 rounded-xl border" value={profile.email} onChange={(e) => updateProfile({ email: e.target.value })} placeholder="you@example.com" />
            </label>
            <label className="grid gap-1">
              <span className="text-sm">髮ｻ隧ｱ逡ｪ蜿ｷ</span>
              <input className="px-3 py-2 rounded-xl border" value={profile.phone ?? ""} onChange={(e) => updateProfile({ phone: e.target.value })} placeholder="090-XXXX-XXXX" />
            </label>
            <div className="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <label className="grid gap-1">
                <span className="text-sm">髢｢蠢・き繝・ざ繝ｪ</span>
                <input className="px-3 py-2 rounded-xl border" value={profile.preferredCategory ?? ""} onChange={(e) => updateProfile({ preferredCategory: e.target.value })} placeholder="遞主漁 / 螂醍ｴ・/ 逶ｸ邯・縺ｪ縺ｩ" />
              </label>
              <label className="grid gap-1">
                <span className="text-sm">繧ｨ繝ｪ繧｢</span>
                <input className="px-3 py-2 rounded-xl border" value={profile.area ?? ""} onChange={(e) => updateProfile({ area: e.target.value })} placeholder="蜷榊商螻・/ 諢帷衍 縺ｪ縺ｩ" />
              </label>
            </div>
            <div className="flex items-center gap-6 pt-2">
              <label className="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
                <input type="checkbox" checked={profile.notificationEmail} onChange={(e) => updateProfile({ notificationEmail: e.target.checked })} />
                繝｡繝ｼ繝ｫ騾夂衍
              </label>
              <label className="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
                <input type="checkbox" checked={profile.notificationPush} onChange={(e) => updateProfile({ notificationPush: e.target.checked })} />
                繝励ャ繧ｷ繝･騾夂衍
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      )}
    </main>
  );
}

===== BEGIN: src\app\session\page.tsx =====
// src/app/session/page.tsx
"use client";

import { useEffect, useMemo, useState } from "react";
import { useRouter } from "next/navigation";
import Link from "next/link";
import { EXPERTS } from "@/data/experts";

type Invite = {
  id: string;         // 繝√Ε繝・ヨID・・chat/[id]・・  expertId: string;   // 蜿励￠縺ｦ繧ゅｉ縺・◆縺・ｰる摩螳ｶ
  clientName: string; // 萓晞ｼ閠・錐
  topic: string;      // 逶ｸ隲・ユ繝ｼ繝・  createdAt: number;  // 逋ｺ陦梧凾蛻ｻ
  ttlSec: number;     // 譛牙柑譛滄剞・育ｧ抵ｼ・  unread: number;     // 譛ｪ隱ｭ謨ｰ・医Δ繝・け・・  note?: string;      // 陬懆ｶｳ
};

const TTL_DEFAULT = 180;                 // 3蛻・const BC_NAME = "sc-inbox";
const LS_KEY = "sc_inbox_new";          // /inbox 蛛ｴ縺梧鏡縺・く繝ｼ

export default function SessionRoomPage() {
  const router = useRouter();

  const [expertId, setExpertId] = useState(EXPERTS[0]?.id ?? "1");
  const [clientName, setClientName] = useState("・医≠縺ｪ縺溘・蜷榊燕・・);
  const [topic, setTopic] = useState("莉翫☆縺千嶌隲・＠縺溘＞莉ｶ縺後≠繧翫∪縺・);
  const [note, setNote] = useState("");
  const [ttl, setTtl] = useState(TTL_DEFAULT);

  // Hydration蟾ｮ蛻・屓驕ｿ縺ｮ縺溘ａ繧ｯ繝ｩ繧､繧｢繝ｳ繝亥愛螳壹＠縺ｦ縺九ｉ陦ｨ遉ｺ
  const [canBC, setCanBC] = useState<boolean | null>(null);
  useEffect(() => {
    try {
      setCanBC(typeof window !== "undefined" && "BroadcastChannel" in window);
    } catch {
      setCanBC(false);
    }
  }, []);

  // 驕ｸ謚樔ｸｭ縺ｮ蟆る摩螳ｶ
  const expert = useMemo(() => EXPERTS.find((e) => e.id === expertId), [expertId]);

  // ID逕滓・・・rypto.randomUUID 縺後≠繧後・菴ｿ縺・ｼ・  const genId = () => {
    try {
      if (typeof crypto !== "undefined" && "randomUUID" in crypto) {
        return crypto.randomUUID();
      }
    } catch {}
    return `${Date.now()}-${Math.random().toString(36).slice(2)}`;
  };

  // 騾∽ｿ｡蜃ｦ逅・ｼ・inbox 縺ｸ騾夂衍竊・/chat/[id] 縺ｸ驕ｷ遘ｻ・医Δ繝・け・・  const startLive = () => {
    const now = Date.now();
    const id = genId();

    const payload: Invite = {
      id,
      expertId,
      clientName: clientName.trim() || "蛹ｿ蜷阪Θ繝ｼ繧ｶ繝ｼ",
      topic: topic.trim() || "逶ｸ隲・′縺ゅｊ縺ｾ縺・,
      createdAt: now,
      ttlSec: Math.max(30, Math.min(600, Number(ttl) || TTL_DEFAULT)),
      unread: 1,
      note: note.trim() || undefined,
    };

    // 1) BroadcastChannel
    try {
      if (canBC) {
        const ch = new BroadcastChannel(BC_NAME);
        ch.postMessage({ type: "add", ...payload });
        ch.close();
      }
    } catch {
      // noop
    }

    // 2) localStorage・・inbox 蛻晏屓繧ｪ繝ｼ繝励Φ譎ゅ・菫晞匱・・    try {
      const prev = localStorage.getItem(LS_KEY);
      const arr: Invite[] = prev ? JSON.parse(prev) : [];
      arr.unshift(payload);
      localStorage.setItem(LS_KEY, JSON.stringify(arr));
    } catch {
      // noop
    }

    // 3) 萓晞ｼ閠・・縺ｯ縺吶＄繝√Ε繝・ヨ逕ｻ髱｢縺ｸ・医Ν繝ｼ繧ｿ繝ｼ縺ｧ驕ｷ遘ｻ・・    router.push(`/chat/${encodeURIComponent(id)}`);
  };

  return (
    <main className="sc-container py-8">
      <h1>繧ｻ繝・す繝ｧ繝ｳ繝ｫ繝ｼ繝・医Δ繝・け・・/h1>
      <p className="mt-1 text-subtle">
        縺薙％縺九ｉ縲後Λ繧､繝也嶌隲・阪ｒ髢句ｧ九＠縺ｾ縺吶ゆｽ懈・縺輔ｌ縺滓魚蠕・・ <code>/inbox</code> 縺ｫ螻翫″縲・        譛牙柑譛滄剞・域里螳・蛻・ｼ峨・髢薙↓蟆る摩螳ｶ縺悟女縺代ｋ縺ｨ <code>/chat/[id]</code> 縺ｫ謗･邯壹＠縺ｾ縺吶・      </p>

      <form
        onSubmit={(e) => {
          e.preventDefault();
          startLive();
        }}
        className="mt-6 grid gap-4 card p-5"
      >
        {/* 逶ｸ謇具ｼ亥ｰる摩螳ｶ・・*/}
        <div>
          <label className="text-sm">逶ｸ謇具ｼ亥ｰる摩螳ｶ・・/label>
          <select
            value={expertId}
            onChange={(e) => setExpertId(e.target.value)}
            className="mt-1 select"
            aria-label="逶ｸ謇具ｼ亥ｰる摩螳ｶ・峨ｒ驕ｸ謚・
          >
            {EXPERTS.map((e) => (
              <option key={e.id} value={e.id}>
                {e.name}・・e.license ?? "雉・ｼ縺ｪ縺・}・閲e.online ? " / 蠕・ｩ滉ｸｭ" : ""}
              </option>
            ))}
          </select>
        </div>

        {/* 萓晞ｼ閠・錐 */}
        <div>
          <label className="text-sm">縺ゅ↑縺溘・陦ｨ遉ｺ蜷・/label>
          <input
            value={clientName}
            onChange={(e) => setClientName(e.target.value)}
            className="mt-1 input"
            placeholder="萓具ｼ画ｪ蠑丈ｼ夂､ｾ縲・・莉｣陦ｨ"
          />
        </div>

        {/* 逶ｸ隲・ユ繝ｼ繝・*/}
        <div>
          <label className="text-sm">逶ｸ隲・ユ繝ｼ繝橸ｼ医・縺ｨ縺薙→縺ｧ・・/label>
          <input
            value={topic}
            onChange={(e) => setTopic(e.target.value)}
            className="mt-1 input"
            placeholder="萓具ｼ画ｱｺ邂怜燕縺ｮ遽遞弱メ繧ｧ繝・け"
          />
        </div>

        {/* 陬懆ｶｳ */}
        <div>
          <label className="text-sm">陬懆ｶｳ・井ｻｻ諢擾ｼ・/label>
          <textarea
            value={note}
            onChange={(e) => setNote(e.target.value)}
            rows={3}
            className="mt-1 textarea"
            placeholder="邁｡蜊倥↑閭梧勹繧・・譛峨＠縺溘＞雉・侭縺ｮ讎りｦ√↑縺ｩ"
          />
        </div>

        {/* TTL */}
        <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
          <label className="text-sm">譛牙柑譛滄剞・育ｧ抵ｼ・/label>
          <input
            type="number"
            min={30}
            max={600}
            value={ttl}
            onChange={(e) => setTtl(Number(e.target.value))}
            className="w-28 input"
          />
          <span className="text-sm text-muted">窶ｻ 謗ｨ螂ｨ 180 遘抵ｼ・蛻・ｼ・/span>
        </div>

        {/* 騾∽ｿ｡ */}
        <div className="mt-2 flex gap-2">
          <button type="submit" className="btn btn-primary flex-1">
            繝ｩ繧､繝也嶌隲・ｒ髢句ｧ・          </button>
          <Link href="/inbox" className="btn btn-outline">
            蜿嶺ｿ｡邂ｱ・亥ｰる摩螳ｶ蛛ｴ・峨ｒ隕九ｋ
          </Link>
        </div>

        {/* 迥ｶ諷玖｡ｨ遉ｺ */}
        <div className="text-xs text-subtle">
          謗･邯壽婿蠑擾ｼ咤roadcastChannel{" "}
          {canBC === null ? "蛻､螳壻ｸｭ窶ｦ" : canBC ? "菴ｿ逕ｨ蜿ｯ" : "荳榊庄・・ocalStorage 邨檎罰縺ｫ繝輔か繝ｼ繝ｫ繝舌ャ繧ｯ・・}
        </div>

        {/* 驕ｸ謚樔ｸｭ縺ｮ蟆る摩螳ｶ縺ｮ陬懆ｶｳ・井ｻｻ諢剰｡ｨ遉ｺ・・*/}
        {expert && (
          <div className="divider" aria-hidden />
        )}
      </form>
    </main>
  );
}

===== END: src\app\session\page.tsx =====
